{"tid":1351851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27/7唔係淨係勇武嘅事！！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:04:31.000Z","uid":110808,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4c3338403132915b1f2c4cac8d55ff3d3d1646","tid":1351851,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:35:50.000Z","msg":"利伸 元朗人 非村民 發夢<br />\n<br />\n721好多人臨時入元朗 <br />\n但本身個個都係出面忙左成日又攰加唔熟路<br />\n結果就係港島少左人少左關注 元朗又唔夠警鄉黑打<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727唔建議分兩區行動 </span></span><br />\n如果唔係同721一樣兩邊都俾人㩒住打<br />\n<br />\n上環手足絕對唔係condom<br />\n大家諗清楚727入元朗係為乜 唔係淨係爛仔報仇<br />\n黑社會互毆成日都有 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">問題係警黑合作</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以727要繼續貼題 <span style=\"color: red;\">承接5大訴求</span><br />\n個人覺得元朗都唔止得勇武一條路<br />\n勇武嘅就真係對村民 會係元朗東面(Yoho,西鐵站南邊圍一帶)<br />\n主要係有心理準備 有能力有體力嘅前線人員<br />\n有顧慮嘅絲打唔好諗 唔好勉強自己<br />\n<br />\n同時實行和理非方案<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">包圍元朗警署 </span></span><br />\n唔好俾佢地落閂 要佢地出返黎面對執行本身嘅責任 (即俾壓力佢出警力去阻止鄉黑打人)<br />\nBtw警署隔離就係警察宿舍 人多就圍埋佢<br />\n如果有鄉黑黎到當然要抵抗<br />\n但至少俾班人睇至事實係點<br />\n<br />\n求連登軍司加入討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0926cfc92a61290d756e5ea1ca611b1bb532ef","tid":1351851,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gzKOfg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gzKOfg.png&h=d524b086&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJgUq1W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJgUq1W.png&h=73b3f8e8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96G9eVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96G9eVh.png&h=a86b52e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPZnzVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPZnzVh.png&h=07b87c18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqWtvtD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqWtvtD.png&h=6e2036a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c727e8ea882f84047b15e9b130ef0f13d72d1807","tid":1351851,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:37:26.000Z","msg":"識我唔好爆我出黎！"},{"pid":"34f69da132a0de25f0420e0d88485444456dfa9a","tid":1351851,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇落OK"},{"pid":"e6928844db0e166b8114967725c40b9b13e8bce2","tid":1351851,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"我知出面講緊追究721出槍<br />\n但淨係輿論係唔夠<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要將727個行動都扣題！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"3551e47c3eec95095dcb71e415a19cd8b1a8f47b","tid":1351851,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:42:25.000Z","msg":"上次係輸仲信警察！"},{"pid":"d5117d0ad5d4bdcaa40c87585ee647810f6432d9","tid":1351851,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f293c7f7e317b6c1e3c2d8950c07fdd39021825","tid":1351851,"uid":280783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b3d8a3737fbfe73c7128f754833bfe0cdc68d0","tid":1351851,"uid":110808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f293c7f7e317b6c1e3c2d8950c07fdd39021825","tid":1351851,"uid":280783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:52:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:00:29